    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "No To Tie-Dye",
        "Description": "Known drug smuggler Torres Piombo is in the process of acquiring an extremely dangerous substance from a plant native to Ambrose Island. He is scheduled to deliver to a Mr. Safin, who according to British Intelligence intends to create a toxic bioweapon with it. As such, MI6 has issued a new &quot;no tie-dye&quot; policy.\rYou are to launch an assault on the militia&apos;s jungle encampment. Eliminate the mule as well as two soldiers assigned to protect Piombo.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as magicdave94.",
